graph TD
    A[GET /move-hatch Request] --> B[Execute with Error Handling]
    B --> C[Check current hatch state]
    C --> D{Is hatch currently open?}
    D -- No, hatch is closed --> E[Log: Opening hatch]
    D -- Yes, hatch is open --> F[Log: Closing hatch]
    E --> G[Command hatch to open]
    F --> H[Command hatch to close]
    G --> I[Return success response with new hatch state]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Request Complete]
